      "rationale": "Validation scenario uses production-representative non-cannulated 7.5 mm screw geometry, ASTM F1717 test block fixtures, and quasi-static compression-bending loading — directly matching the COU. The single test condition gap (Test conditions factor) is the only identified deviation from full COU relevance."
    }
